OL,6,FA planned strike at Southampton
OL,7,FAirport has been called off after a
OL,8,Fpay deal was agreed.
OL,10,FCrew commanders, firefighters and
OL,11,Fmulti-skilled technicians were due to
OL,12,Fwalk out on Friday, (16 February) but
OL,13,Ffollowing the acceptance of the
OL,14,Fimproved offer by members all
OL,15,Findustrial action has now been called
OL,16,Foff.
